OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunshine in
OL,6,Fthe south this evening, cloudier in
OL,7,Fthe north. A few showers overnight but
OL,8,Fmost places staying dry. A warm and
OL,9,Fmuggy night with temperatures in the
OL,10,Fhigh-teens.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FThe odd shower in the north
OL,13,Fto start, otherwise sunny on Tuesday
OL,14,Fwith blue skies and strong sunshine.
OL,15,FVery hot and humid, particularly in
OL,16,Fsouthern parts of the region.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
